description: Green Growth Brands Inc., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the cultivation, processing, production, distribution, and retailing of cannabis and cannabidiol (CBD)-infused consumer products in the United States. It provides medical and retail marijuana products to various dispensaries; and CBD-infused personal care and beauty products, such as therapeutic, face care, body care, shower and bathroom, and sleep products through shops, e-commerce, and wholesale channels. The company offers its products under the CAMP, Seventh Sense Botanical Therapy, The+Source, Green Lily, and Meri + Jayne brand names. The company was formerly known as Xanthic Biopharma Inc. and changed its name to Green Growth Brands Inc. in January 2019. Green Growth Brands Inc. was founded in 1968 and is based in Columbus, Ohio.
